high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a right, go to the black shelf where the newspaper is.
Pick up the newspaper from the shelf.
Turn around and go to the black chair.
Put the newspaper in the black chair.
Turn to the left, go forward to the couch on the right where the newspaper is.
Pick up the newspaper from the couch.
Turn to the right, go to the black chair on the left, turn around and face the chair.
Put the newspaper on the chair to the right of the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers in a chair.

high_descs: Turn right, turn right at the wall, look down at the shelf.
Pick up the newspaper from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the black chair across the room.
Put the newspaper down on the chair.
Turn left and walk to the couch on the right.
Pick up the newspaper from the left side of the box.
Walk back over to the black chair.
Put the newspaper down on the chair to the right of the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: To move two newspapers to the black chair.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the wall at the end of the room, then turn right and go to the black shelf.
Pick up the newspaper on the left of the black shelf in front of you.
Turn around and go to the arm chair, across the room from you.
Place the newspaper on the left side of the seat of the chair.
Turn to your left and go to the middle of the couch ahead, to your right.
Pick up the newspaper between the computer and the cardboard box, on the couch.
Turn to your right and go back to the chair across the room, on your left.
Place the newspaper on the seat of the chair to the right of the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on the living room chair.
